Jamie Dorrington https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jamie_Dorrington 0 Jamie Dorrington (born 1984 in Leeds) is a British actor who is best known for his role in the English crime drama Happy Valley alongside Sarah Lancashire He also features in BBC's To Walk Invisible Playing Enoch Thomas and Channel 4 Drama Series Ackley Bridge(2017) Plus many other British films.
